  "3263210": {
    "name": "电车除灵少女",
    "steam_appid": 3263210,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263210/extras/7a1df6db79581a59091bda6ec824a2c9.avif?t=1739206955\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263210/extras_big/7a1df6db79581a59091bda6ec824a2c9.avif?t=1739206955 width=800 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《电车除灵少女》是一款由<strong>一人开发、RPGmaker mv引擎制作</strong>、受《8番出口》启发的 <strong>小体量 </strong>悬疑恐怖游戏，游戏具有一定的“肉鸽”随机要素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>*游戏采用RPGmaker mv制作，因引擎限制，操作手感、演出效果等有各种各样的问题。</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>*游戏为一人制作、首次开发，体量较小。</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>*游戏特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263210/extras/c14344e49e5658dda230cadc63f87820.avif?t=1739206955\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263210/extras_big/c14344e49e5658dda230cadc63f87820.avif?t=1739206955 width=800 height=491 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏具有一定随机要素，你无法预知接下来将遇到什么恐怖现象。每次的死亡重生，都将面临完全不同的新的危机状况，之前探索的经验无法帮助到你、带给你安全感。随机出现的恐怖灵异状况和怪物更让人胆战心惊。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家必须找出所有的异状并设法消除，确保自己没有疏漏，才能安全抵达终点，否则将被不可名状的未知邪恶力量不断击杀并重生。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏在恐怖悬疑及轻度Rogue like的玩法基础上，拥有一定的剧情叙事与角色塑造，恐怖阴暗的地铁电车中充满了未知与谜团，玩家在其中探索与各种角色、怪物、异状互动对话，以获得身临其境的角色扮演体验与故事体会。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中将出现令人耳目一新的的怪物设计与诡异异常的恐怖形象，游戏致力于塑造强烈的心理恐怖氛围与难以理解的恐怖景象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断到来的未知和惊奇，你敢挑战吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263210/extras/815af7850a7384a256a861090b164d16.avif?t=1739206955\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263210/extras_big/815af7850a7384a256a861090b164d16.avif?t=1739206955 width=800 height=405 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
